events="//// QueryViewer sample code
Event Start
	&UserId = GetUserId()
	DynamicComponent.Visible = false
	QueryViewer.Visible = false
Endevent

Event ClientStart		
	&ClientId = ClientInformation.Id
Endevent

Event 'Back'
	GridSent.Visible = true
	DynamicComponent.Visible = false
	BackBtn.Visible = false
Endevent

//Messages Grid
Event GridSent.Load
	QueryViewer.Visible = false
	Do Case
		Case GXChatMessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.UserImage
			GridSent.ItemLayout = ChatbotLayouts.AskImage
		Case GXChatMessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.User
			GridSent.ItemLayout = ChatbotLayouts.Ask
		Case GXChatMessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.ResponseImage
			GridSent.ItemLayout = ChatbotLayouts.ResponseImage
		Case GXChatMessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.Response
			GridSent.ItemLayout = ChatbotLayouts.Response
		Case GXChatMessageType = ChatbotMessageTypes.ResponsePanel
			GridSent.ItemLayout = ChatbotLayouts.ResponsePanel
		Case GXChatMessageType = Chatbotmessagetypes.Query
			GridSent.ItemLayout = ChatbotLayouts.Query
			Do 'SetQueryViewer'
			
	EndCase
Endevent

//Messaging Events
Event 'EnterSend'
	Do 'SendMessage'
Endevent

Event SendIcon.Tap
	Do 'SendMessage'
Endevent

Event GlobalEvents.EnumeratedEvent(&EventsMessage)
	&Send = &EventsMessage
	Do 'SendMessage'
Endevent

Event GlobalEvents.BotEvent(&EventsMessage)
	&Send = &EventsMessage
	Do 'SendMessage'
Endevent

Event GXChatMessageRepeat.Tap
	Composite
		GetComponentById(GXChatMessageId, &SDComponentLink, &IsCallPanel)
		Do 'SDActions'
	Endcomposite
Endevent

//Messaging subs
Sub 'SendMessage' //Send Message
	Do 'SetImage'
	BackBtn.Visible = false
	&Image.Visible = false
	BackBtn.Visible = false
	DynamicComponent.Visible = false	
	CommonChatbots.SendMessage(&Instance, ChatbotPlatform.SmartDevices, &MessageToSend, &SendImage, &ClientId)
EndSub	

Event GeneXus.Client.Socket.MessageReceived(&MessageReceived)
	Composite
		&NotificationInfo.FromJson(&MessageReceived)
		Do Case 
			Case &NotificationInfo.Id = ChatbotNotificationTypes.ChatbotMessage
				GridSent.Refresh()
			Case &NotificationInfo.Id = ChatbotNotificationTypes.ChatbotError
				&Messages.FromJson(&NotificationInfo.Message)
				&ShowErrorsInUI = ErrorHandling(&Messages)
				if &ShowErrorsInUI				
					msg(&Messages.ToJson())
				endif			
		EndCase
	EndComposite
EndEvent

//Components
Sub 'SDActions'
	if not &SDComponentLink.IsEmpty()
		if not &IsCallPanel
			DynamicComponent.Object = CreateFromURL(&SDComponentLink)
			GridSent.Visible = false
			DynamicComponent.Visible = true
			BackBtn.Visible = true
		else
			DynamicComponent.Visible = false
			Call(&SDComponentLink)
		endif
	else
		DynamicComponent.Visible = false
	endif
EndSub

//Images Events
Event GXChatMessageImage.Tap
	Composite
		Do 'ShowMessageImage'
		PanelShowImage(GXChatMessageImage)
	Endcomposite
Endevent

Event Gallery.Tap
	Composite
		&Image = SD.Media.PhotoLibrary.ChooseImage()
		Do 'ShowUserImage'
	Endcomposite
Endevent

//Images Subs
Sub 'SetImage' //New Message
	if &Image.IsEmpty()
		&SendImage.SetEmpty()
	else
		if &Send.IsEmpty()
			&Send = !"Image"
		endif
		&SendImage = &Image
		&Image.SetEmpty()
		&Image.Visible = false		
	endif	
	&MessageToSend = &Send
	&Send = ""
	GridSent.Visible = true
EndSub

Sub 'ShowUserImage'
	GridSent.Visible = false
	&Image.Visible = true
EndSub

Sub 'ShowImage' //Show Image	
	Do 'SetCallType'
	&TargetHeight = '25%'
	&TargetWidth = '50%'	
	Do 'SetHeightWidth'
EndSub

Sub 'ShowMessageImage'
	Do 'SetCallType'
	&TargetHeight = '75%'
	&TargetWidth= '75%'
	Do 'SetHeightWidth'
EndSub

Sub 'SetHeightWidth'
	PanelShowImage.CallOptions.TargetHeight = &TargetHeight
	PanelShowImage.CallOptions.TargetWidth = &TargetWidth
EndSub

Sub 'SetCallType'
	PanelShowImage.CallOptions.Type = CallType.Callout
	PanelShowImage.CallOptions.EnterEffect = Effect.Fade
EndSub

//Query Events
Sub 'SetQueryViewer'
	QueryViewer.Visible = true
	&Parameters.Clear()		
	GetQueryComponentById(GXChatMessageId, &QueryName, &Parameters, &ViewType) 
	
	QueryViewer.ObjectName = &QueryName
	
	if &ViewType <> ""
		if &ViewType = QueryViewerOutputType.Table or &ViewType = QueryViewerOutputType.PivotTable
			QueryViewer.Type = &ViewType
		else
			QueryViewer.Type = QueryViewerOutputType.Chart
			QueryViewer.ChartType = &ViewType
		endif
	else
		QueryViewer.Type = QueryViewerOutputType.Default
	endif	
	QueryViewer.Refresh()
EndSub
Event FullSize.Tap
	Composite
		Do 'ShowQueryViewer'
		PanelShowQueryViewer(GXChatMessageId)
	EndComposite
EndEvent

Sub 'ShowQueryViewer'
	Do 'SetCallTypeQuery'
	&TargetHeight = '75%'
	&TargetWidth= '75%'
	Do 'SetHeightWidthQuery'
EndSub

Sub 'SetHeightWidthQuery'
	PanelShowQueryViewer.CallOptions.TargetHeight = &TargetHeight
	PanelShowQueryViewer.CallOptions.TargetWidth = &TargetWidth
EndSub

Sub 'SetCallTypeQuery'
	PanelShowQueryViewer.CallOptions.Type = CallType.Callout
	PanelShowQueryViewer.CallOptions.EnterEffect = Effect.Fade
EndSub
